name: Selling Sunset
overview: The elite agents at The Oppenheim Group sell the luxe life to affluent buyers in LA. Relationships are everything, and that often means major drama.

episodes.name: If Looks Could Sell
episodes.overview: New agent Chrishell joins The Oppenheim Group and realizes she must prove herself. The brokers square off to sell a spectacular Hollywood Hills home

episodes.name: Can't Have Your Cake and Eat It Too
episodes.overview: The agents get real about juggling love and career. Mary is shaken at her anniversary dinner. Heather feels the distance from Nick -- and Christine.

episodes.name: (Real) Diamonds Are a Girl's Best Friend
episodes.overview: Mary gets a big surprise as Christine finds herself in an unexpected fight -- and date. Actor Taye Diggs tours a home. Heather copes with a crisis.

episodes.name: Loose Lips Sink Relationships
episodes.overview: Chrishell learns a few lessons about business and friendship while Heather takes flak for delays. Maya makes a discovery but needs to keep it secret.

episodes.name: The One That Got Away
episodes.overview: Heather and Christine face off over the firm's big deal as Mary tries to find common ground. Christine warns Chrishell: Secrets set off explosions.

episodes.name: Real Estate Hunger Games
episodes.overview: A client pits Chrishell and Christine against each other. Heather sells her hot property and eyes a buyer for the unique home in the Hollywood Hills.

episodes.name: It Takes Two to Make a Thing Go Right
episodes.overview: Relationships are everything as Chrishell struggles to find an ideal home for a demanding buyer. Christine and Heather try to work together on a deal.

episodes.name: The Gloves Come Off
episodes.overview: Chrishell encounters jealousy as Heather embarrasses Jason. Mary reveals her frustration, and simmering tensions come to a full boil at the big party.

episodes.name: Let the Real Estate Games Begin
episodes.overview: The agents catch up at the $44 million home and learn Christine's engaged. Heather reveals a romance. Chrishell works the Valley. Amanza arrives.

episodes.name: Billionaires Have Compounds
episodes.overview: Chrishell and Christine have it out. Mary finds a dream home, and Davina thinks big. News of Heather's latest love leads to a frank talk with Brett.

episodes.name: Sorry, Not Sorry
episodes.overview: Heather and Amanza connect before Romain drops a bombshell. Chrishell gets a key listing as Christine plans her engagement party and spills to Davina.

episodes.name: The Red Engagement Party
episodes.overview: A stressed Mary must secure a wedding venue stat. Chrishell and Christine consider the unthinkable. Tempers flare at a red-hot engagement party.

episodes.name: I'm No Soldier
episodes.overview: Chrishell tours Jason's celebrity-owned home for her star client. Mary confronts Christine and battles the boss. Maya checks out Brett's project.

episodes.name: The Wait Will Be Worth the Wait
episodes.overview: Retail therapy gives Christine a chance to vent. Mary shops for her ideal wedding dress. Amanza tries to help Heather, but can she do anything right?

episodes.name: That's Why They Call It Real Estress
episodes.overview: Amanza confides in Mary. Davina ponders an invitation. The agents dish the dirt in Los Feliz. After hours, the bachelorette bash seethes with drama.

episodes.name: Karma's Gonna Get You
episodes.overview: The realtors get real and revisit the "overlap" flap. Tears at a broker's open lead to a blowout. On her big day, Mary juggles her work and wedding.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Luxe properties. Fabulous views. Enormous stakes. The agents of The Oppenheim Group mix business and pleasure — with maximum drama.

episodes.name: Back to Business
episodes.overview: Amanza breaks down the backstabbing. After touring a sexy new listing and getting a tarot reading, Christine lashes back at her birthday bash.

episodes.name: Confidence Is Key
episodes.overview: Business is booming, but Jason isn't happy with Amanza. Brokers turn out for Christine's burgers and Botox blowout. Alone, Chrishell and Davina clash.

episodes.name: The Biggest Agent in the Room
episodes.overview: Tensions grow over a high-priced listing, and fissures appear in a friendship. Heather and Amanza warily team up. Mary makes a confession to Romain.

episodes.name: Everybody Loves Mary
episodes.overview: The agents dish about favoritism and weigh their options. Heather and Amanza get — and give — some bad news. Friendsgiving brings a huge announcement.

episodes.name: Bad News Travels Fast
episodes.overview: A "Versace house" is on the agenda. Christine falls for a wedding gown. Two agents try to talk it out. After Chrishell's event, shocking news breaks.

episodes.name: One Text Changes Everything
episodes.overview: Still raw, Chrishell confides in Mary. Christine, Maya and Davina meet for tea. Mary faces Romain. Amanza and Heather's teamwork makes for dream work.

episodes.name: Two Sides to Every Story
episodes.overview: It takes two. Chrishell regroups and reassesses in St. Louis as Christine gets set for her wedding. After all her hard work, Amanza clinches a deal.

episodes.name: A Not So White Wedding
episodes.overview: Chrishell returns. Heather bristles. After showing a Neutra to "Queer Eye" star Karamo, Christine walks down the aisle. Unanticipated drama awaits.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: Big changes come to The Oppenheim Group as a major sale closes, the women consider career moves, and one agent faces a very public breakup.

episodes.name: Very High Heels to Fill
episodes.overview: An expecting Christine and revived Chrishell eye sexy, luxe properties. A hot market means major growth as disarming new agent Vanessa joins the team.

episodes.name: New Friends, Old Enemies
episodes.overview: Drama looms following a tour of French Montana's opulent digs when Vanessa bonds with Christine and then connects with Chrishell, Heather and Mary.

episodes.name: Rival Arrival
episodes.overview: Jason breaks the news: Emma will fill her rival's sky-high heels. Chrishell fights to buy her first home. Christine talks about a tough childbirth.

episodes.name: The Emma Dilemma
episodes.overview: Another dinner, another dramatic reveal: Emma tells her side of the story. Amid spectacular views, Vanessa tries to get to the truth with Christine.

episodes.name: Let Sleeping Dogs Lie
episodes.overview: Christine flexes for Davina, who reaches out to Jason. After a splashy sale goes south, a familiar face crashes Mary's canine birthday celebration.

episodes.name: A House for a Hero
episodes.overview: Newly minted superhero Simu Liu gets the star treatment as Chrishell's client. Christine and Emma try to clear the air. Davina negotiates a return.

episodes.name: Back on the Market
episodes.overview: Agents bring the heart — and movers, the heat — to the once-homeless Chrishell's housewarming. Amanza reveals her troubles, and a date grows awkward.

episodes.name: The Truth Hurts
episodes.overview: Chrishell takes Simu on a hero's journey through a gamer's retreat. Heather makes a tearful decision. Christine surprises Maya as Amanza gets a shock.

episodes.name: The Beginning of the End
episodes.overview: Open house, open book: Davina faces Christine, who meets Vanessa's mindset coach. Chrishell works with player Thomas Bryant. Mary and Romain clash.

episodes.name: One Last Hail Mary
episodes.overview: Anticipation builds for Jason's lavish bash. Chrishell finds an ideal house for Thomas. Big news drops, but will Christine drop her defenses for Mary?

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: The booming real estate market keeps the agents on their toes while new and returning teammates stir up the drama, and celebrity clients come calling.

episodes.name: Game Changer
episodes.overview: Flying high: Chrishell reveals her latest love — Jason. In LA, the agents get real about the relationship while Christine readies her return.

episodes.name: New Blood
episodes.overview: At the office, Chrishell faces J-Shell questions. Chelsea connects with Jason. Christine dishes with Amanza. Emma shocks, and Mary gets big news.

episodes.name: Coming for All Your Coin
episodes.overview: Black and blond Barbies brainstorm. Emma meets a hot developer with a sexy home. Chrishell tries out a dog door. Heather's shower ends with a surprise.

episodes.name: Bad Bitches Don't Cry
episodes.overview: Heather has it out, but can Christine keep it professional? At the caviar and couture party, Chelsea dresses to impress and defends her friend.

episodes.name: Do You Think We're Friends?
episodes.overview: Emma shares a new love with Chrishell. Christine breaks down her event, Amanza reveals an empowering space, and Davina clashes with a client.

episodes.name: Step Up or Step Out
episodes.overview: Hot market, high expectations: Mary ups the pressure and makes a confession to Romain. Chrishell spars with Brett. Davina looks for a last chance.

episodes.name: It's Getting Personal
episodes.overview: Real talk: Chelsea hears from Heather while Davina confronts Christine about her catty quips. Jason's mom grills Chrishell and her son over bites.

episodes.name: She's Your Problem Too
episodes.overview: Musical desks: Chelsea enters blazing, bearing business and invites. Mary makes her move. Chrishell confides in Jason. A tea party gets heated.

episodes.name: Sabotage in Stilettos
episodes.overview: Miami-bound Maya goes out with a bang. Spilt tea leaves Davina unsettled. Chrishell opens up to Heather. A backstabbing rumor shakes Mary.

episodes.name: Nothing Remains The Same
episodes.overview: Hearts flip as Heather weds Tarek. Jason and Mary grapple with being ghosted. Go solo or take the next step: The agents face life-changing decisions.

episodes.name: The Reunion
episodes.overview: Fractured friendships. Telling texts. Raw emotions. Hot gossip. The cast sit down with host Tan France to talk about the season and their lives today.

5.name: Season 5
5.overview: New loves. Old foes. A fresh face. With the luxury market on fire, competition comes to a boil at the brokerage. Who'll shine — and who'll stumble?

episodes.name: I Wanted to Hate You
episodes.overview: Chrishell is head-over-heels in love — but is she ready to face the awkwardness at the office? New agent Bre comes in hot, ruffling a few feathers.

episodes.name: TBD on Bre
episodes.overview: While old resentments threaten to create new drama between Chrishell and veteran Oppenheim agent Nicole, Chelsea raises some doubts about Bre.

episodes.name: Old Deals Die Hard
episodes.overview: A smitten Jason introduces the team to his girlfriend, Marie-Lou, and asks Mary for a favor. The claws come out at a Manhattan Beach open house.

episodes.name: Between You and Bre
episodes.overview: After a girls' night out for Heather's birthday, Chelsea shares her unfiltered opinions about Bre's relationship. Mary urges Nicole to make peace.

episodes.name: Miss Management
episodes.overview: Bre shows houses to a celebrity client looking for a fabulous family home, while renovation delays and office squabbling amp up Mary's anxiety levels.

episodes.name: Mary in the Middle
episodes.overview: Jason has a rocky reentry from Europe, prompting Emma to complain to Chrishell. Mary attempts to facilitate peace talks.

episodes.name: If You Can't Stand the Heat...
episodes.overview: Chrishell and Jason catch up before the agents head to Palm Springs for what they hope is a healing retreat — but leaving the drama in LA won't be easy.

episodes.name: Bre Bites Back
episodes.overview: While Elvis superfan Chrishell enjoys a tour of his honeymoon home, Nicole makes a statement. Later, Bre airs out her grievances with Chelsea.

episodes.name: Lawsuits and Listings
episodes.overview: On the agents' last day in Palm Springs, a pool party ceasefire doesn't even last until the end of dinner. Bre tours a listing with rapper Saweetie.

episodes.name: Something's Gotta Give
episodes.overview: Back in LA, Bre opens up to Heather and Amanza shares emotional news with Mary. Heather's baby shower becomes yet another battleground.

episodes.name: It's Not Worth It
episodes.overview: Chelsea shows Emma a new side of herself. At Jason's penthouse launch event, a candid conversation with Mary helps Chrishell come to a realization.

6.name: Season 6
6.overview: The stakes and stilettos are as high as they've ever been at the brokerage, as longtime agents make big changes and two new team members bring the heat.

episodes.name: The Real Estate Apocalypse
episodes.overview: Chrishell and Jason return from New Year's Down Under to a chilly LA real estate market. Chelsea goes big for her 30th birthday with a glam masquerade.

episodes.name: Mean Girl Sh*t
episodes.overview: After conflict with the other agents pushes Nicole to a breaking point, Amanza tries to broker a ceasefire. Jason raises a concern with Chrishell.

episodes.name: House of Horrors
episodes.overview: Chrishell counsels comedian Nikki Glaser and meets Marie-Lou for an awkward lunch. An anniversary dinner at an LA architectural landmark turns tense.

episodes.name: Namaste Out of Everyone's Business
episodes.overview: Chelsea attempts to wipe the slate clean with Bre, but Amanza can't escape the mess. Not everyone is on board with Jason's big plans for a new office.

episodes.name: Setting the Stage for Disaster
episodes.overview: New listing assignments cause friction when Brett ruffles Bre's feathers. Jason asks Nicole to prep a house for Chrishell to sell.

episodes.name: It's Not the Size of the Listing...
episodes.overview: While Chelsea gets to work on her new $10 million listing, Amanza hatches a plan to decorate G Flip's studio. Mary gives Nicole some advice.

episodes.name: Cabo San Loco
episodes.overview: The agents fly south to check out the O Group's new location in Cabo, with all their drama along for the ride. Mary and Romain process a painful loss.

episodes.name: Oppenheim Wine
episodes.overview: An encounter at a Cabo open house puts Bre on edge. Mary joins the party. Amanza loses her patience with Chrishell's vanishing act.

episodes.name: The Enemy of My Enemy
episodes.overview: Back in LA, the fallout from Cabo continues. Chelsea and Nicole find common ground with a new friend. Mary and Chrishell reconnect.

episodes.name: Pack It Up, Pack It In
episodes.overview: Chelsea recommends a potential new agent, raising Bre's eyebrows. While the crew packs up to move offices, Amanza prioritizes self-care.

episodes.name: Commission Impossible
episodes.overview: Bre makes a case for her worth to Jason ahead of a blowout bash for the shiny new Oppenheim office, where old friends and new rivals come face to face.

episodes.name: The Reunion
episodes.overview: Alongside host Tan France, the O Group agents reunite to discuss this season's drama, disputes and difficult truths.

7.name: Season 7
7.overview: The agents hustle to move houses in a tough market, but bad blood and unfinished business could bring down what they've built. Can they keep it together?

episodes.name: The Girls Are Back in Town
episodes.overview: Chelsea calls out Mary for labeling her the biggest instigator in the office. New agent Alanna chases a $30 million listing. Bre puts Jason on the spot.

episodes.name: Who Wears the Pants?
episodes.overview: Chrishell tries to persuade Bre to return to The O Group. Mary criticizes Chelsea's professionalism at an open house. Brett and Jason evaluate Alanna.

episodes.name: Cat's Out of the Birkin Bag
episodes.overview: Amanza throws herself a birthday bash where the drinks and the drama flow freely. Bre's friend Amanda spills a shocking secret about an Oppenheim agent.

episodes.name: Sitting on a Secret
episodes.overview: Chelsea and Mary meet to address their issues head-on as Bre debates whether to share bad news. A tense confrontation at the office rattles Nicole.

episodes.name: Once Alanna Time in the West
episodes.overview: Bre reveals explosive news to Chelsea that affects the group trip to Alanna's Western-themed desert oasis. Nicole brings up a touchy topic at dinner.

episodes.name: Don't Rain on My Parade
episodes.overview: Nicole, Alanna and Amanza tour the iconic Invisible House. Bre helps her ex, Johnny Manziel, find a place. A rainy open house draws an unexpected agent.

episodes.name: Sides Are Chosen
episodes.overview: Chelsea questions Bre's motives for airing her personal news on camera. Alanna's listing turns problematic. Emma pitches an intriguing idea to Chrishell.

episodes.name: Down on Your Potluck
episodes.overview: The team gathers at a memorial potluck for an old friend, where Bre's presence creates tension. Chrishell's attempt at peacekeeping frustrates Chelsea.

episodes.name: Two Listings and a Funeral
episodes.overview: TikTok celebs tap The O Group to list their home, and Jason shops to ease his sorrow. The clash between Bre and Chelsea intensifies in the wrong place.

episodes.name: World War Bre
episodes.overview: Chrishell finds herself in a tricky spot with a client's property. Amanza's packed art show impresses the crew. Bre shares some regrets with Amanda.

episodes.name: Burning Down the House
episodes.overview: Jason stuns the team with a risky investment. Amanza ponders her future while Bre hatches a plot to shake up the office. Chelsea eyes a new home.

8.name: Season 8
8.overview: Glam looks. Fierce clashes. Stunning homes. It's business as usual for The Oppenheim Group as they welcome a new agent and bid farewell to a dear friend.
